name: Portraits from the Multiverse - Female Presidents - Obama
description:
Portraits from the Multiverse is a series of AI-generated works that imagine alternate realities where things are not quite what they are now. Female Presidents shows what the top leaders of the United States would look like if they were women.

You can read about how I created the series here, https://robgon.medium.com/list/portraits-from-the-multiverse-583b06d2130e
